  • Class
    Description
    Endpoints
    Contains both the start and end vertex of a maze to generate.
    MazeGenerator
    Generates mazes (perfect and not perfect) using various algorithms.
    MazeGenEvent
    A step of a maze generation algorithm, contained in a MazeGenLog.
    MazeGenEvent.Connect
    Two vertices of the maze graph have been connected: they are accessible, and the wall between those two is now broken.
    MazeGenEvent.Disconnect
    Two vertices of the maze graph have been disconnected: they are no longer accessible, and the wall between those two is now present.
    MazeGenEvent.SetEndpoints
    Start and end vertices of the maze graph have been set.
    MazeGenLog
    A sequence of maze generation events describing all steps taken during a maze generation algorithm.
    MazeGenResult
    The result of a maze generation algorithm.
